This product includes software developed by the AgentMem project.

The proactive two-phase memory architecture implemented here is a clean-room
reimplementation based on the publicly described method in:

  "Remember When It Matters: Proactive Memory Agent for Long-Horizon Agents"
  arXiv:2607.08716

The design was implemented from the paper's published specification. No source
code from the paper authors' reference repository was copied or adapted.
